spin degrees of freedom in rare-earth\ntitanates and indicate that full orbital degeneracy lifting is associated with\nferromagnetic order.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 22 Nov 2022 16:31:44 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 23 Nov 2022 08:43:44 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-11-24"}
