 the extra space). We also argue that the\nsphaleron-like solution may be regarded as a saddle point of the energy in the\nspace of static field configurations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 23 Nov 2022 04:13:30 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 25 Jan 2023 06:07:35 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-01-26"}
