metry in the microscopic Hamiltonian\nand obtain the temperature dependence of Tan's contact. For the latter, the\npresence of the tri-critical point for $N = 2$ leads to a more pronounced\ntemperature dependence around the transition than for SU($N > 2$)-symmetric\ngases.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 23 Nov 2022 11:39:49 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 23 Jan 2023 10:02:33 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-05-29"}
