resent epoch) from the\nTsujikawa model, i.e $\\vert f'(R_0)-1\\vert < 2.09\\times 10^{-4}$. This bound is\nstronger than those from most of the astrophysical observations and even some\ncosmological observations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 23 Nov 2022 13:45:58 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 27 Mar 2023 15:45:54 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-03-28"}
