olutional networks to dynamically adapt their depths to accommodate an\nincreasing number of interactions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 22 Nov 2022 20:44:28 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 3 Dec 2022 20:02:35 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-12-06"}
