ty in\norigami metamaterials. The proposed experimental technique can be adopted for\ninvestigating other tunable properties of origami metamaterials in static and\nin dynamic regimes, such as finite-strain Poisson's ratios, elastic thermal\nexpansion, and wave propagation control.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 23 Nov 2022 09:17:57 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-11-29"}
